ia:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="563" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/b58d69e0-53d4-11ee-bbb8-327a9e49fc08" width="1000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Amazon]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Echo Dot]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Echo Dot]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Engadget Podcast: iPhone 15 and Apple Watch Series 9 hands-on]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本周，Cherlynn 向我们讲述了她对 Apple iPhone 15 发布会的实际想法。事实证明，iPhone 15 Pro 的钛金属外壳实际上明显更轻！我们也对 Apple Watch Series 9 中的新双击手势感兴趣。（如果它最终训练我们如何使用 Vision Pro 的手势命令，请不要感到惊讶！）</p><p>此外，Engadget 记者 Malek Saleh 也加入讨论她对三星 Galaxy Watch 6 以及戴森可笑的 Zone 空气过滤面罩/耳机的评论。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><hr><p>在下面收听或订阅您选择的播客应用程序。如果您对节目有任何建议或主题，请务必<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="mailto:podcast@engadget.com?subject=Engadget%20Podcast%20Feedback"><strong>给我们发送电子邮件</strong></a>或在评论中留言！请务必查看我们的其他播客， <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-01-engadget-podcasts.html">Engadget News</a> ！ </p><div id="undefined"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:200px;position:relative;"><iframe src="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/GyWZt55" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="art19.com"></iframe></div></div><h2>订阅！</h2><ul><li><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2l0dW5lcy5hcHBsZS5jb20vdXMvcG9kY2FzdC90aGUtZW5nYWRnZXQtcG9kY2FzdC9pZDExNDI3OTA1MzA_bXQ9MiIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZTRhZTc1NzMtZTIxNS00NWM1LWF